Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.12,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}相聚一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:14.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我想打从心里大叫一句 好想快点见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:28.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我相信总有一天 一定能相遇相知永结连理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:44.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}起步走出 希望你能追着我的背影而来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:57.85,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我孤单一人只为等候你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:04.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}落英缤纷的春日午后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:12.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我将祈祷转为誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:27.05,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}但愿你不会忘记最重要的事 永远闪亮动人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去喝酒了是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,喝了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我道歉有什么用?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你自己的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天起有重要的毕业考不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然还有心情去喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦,那是情势所逼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论你会不会毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论你能不能当上褓父
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这种事,我都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能全力以赴 去做你决定的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这样就是最好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想大学毕业的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再稍微认真用功一下如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#86冲击的一夜! 明日菜的莎拉纪念日?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里睡着的话 对身体不太好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是呢 你跑来这里做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又还没有订婚 应该还只是外人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一传出什么奇怪的传闻 你该怎么办呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于订婚的事 我想跟你谈一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我不太清楚订婚究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去问我叔叔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我一直都是 这门亲事的局外人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然不知道订婚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,事到如今…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 我会请我爸妈取消婚约的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取消婚约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:05:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我已经知道你真正的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解…解脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的主人,真是个好女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,我把莎拉放在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰先生,醒一醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三…三鹰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐,请您尽管放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上的事 我不会告诉老爷和夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁做的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那么大家一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈祷五代明年 会有更好的成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油加油,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油加油,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么一副无精打采的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能跟管理员有关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也没有出来送五代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚出了什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代的眼睛红红的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚五代好像没怎么睡 是不是啊,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道,我睡得很熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打了他一巴掌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他喝酒回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我狠狠打了他一巴掌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,你不用在意 是裕作自己不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,谁叫他喝酒回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这么一来 五代肯定毕不了业了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,五代根本不值得同情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然是毕不了业
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的罗 被管理员打了一巴掌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神上一定受到很大的打击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你自己的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想大学毕业的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再稍微认真用功一下如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在等五代回来啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能又跑去哪里喝酒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧,明天还要继续考试耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就是逃跑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,这位老板 现在超低价时段哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,别跑啊,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,景气真差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,五代 你不是请了温书假吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,不过有点状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜我是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们很想我吗? 我马上就能回来陪你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长,陪我玩积木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长,念故事书给我听…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,我一定要毕业 然后当上褓父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果他昨晚没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会去参加毕业考吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦 都被管理员打了一巴掌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代失去奋斗的目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,五代是为了你 才想毕业当上褓父的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种选择职业的方法 未免太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是这种男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是有没有骨气的问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人在偷看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?你去参加毕业考了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天只有考上午
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你昨晚睡在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡在酒家里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上我一个人想了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美 那个鱿鱼干是我想吃的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛那么小气啊,章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是花枝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有没有在听?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 反正回来就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,为了庆祝五代平安回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是要“回来”这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暂时不会回来一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不回来?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想以最佳的状态去考毕业考
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以从今天起 我要住在酒家里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这里也是最佳住处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有酒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了 我偶尔会回来拿换洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,毕业考好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,有什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,人活着坦率最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强的话,都不会有什么好下场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗 千万不要再勉强自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你好好加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰先生,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜留下这封信走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留书出走?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道她失踪了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失踪?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,她是去伊豆的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那我先看看这封信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰先生和我 我们的心情都还没有整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就订婚 我觉得时间有点早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请将订婚的日子延期
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延期?我记得昨天晚上她说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会请我爸妈取消婚约的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果变成延期,意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问发生了什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,没有,没有什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,我想尽快和明日菜小姐 两人单独谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有劝过她了,可是她不肯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚后来的事情 我怎么都想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成那样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道,在那之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很有可能会做出那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:18:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是万一做了的话 我应该勇敢的负起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在九条家 已经当了20年的司机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从明日菜小姐还是婴儿的时候 一直做到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她从小就很坦率诚恳 是个非常善良的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为大小姐是为了袒护你 把一切都藏在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜小姐在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:18:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正在考毕业考,不是吗? 干嘛来住这种地方呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁我的决心还没松动之前 想好好拼一拼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了某人下定决心 一定要毕业当上褓父
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果她不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我毕不了业 连工作也放弃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我自己的存在价值 究竟在哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想先一个人努力看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果自己无法做到 哪有资格去照顾别人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单的说,是你被你马子甩了 还是说你逃了出来?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪一种?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这种事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是逃出来的话 绝对不可以回去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,一定要坚持到她道歉为止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女之间啊 追的那一方才是输家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要拼命的逃 不断的逃,跑给她追
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一她不追过来的话 怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!那时候就要乖乖放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用最快的速度赶回去 向她下跪道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人是很单纯的 他们吃这一套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是逃出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想暂时自己努力看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力试着忘了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在,我相信我办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜小姐,对不起 我无法等到你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,那顿早餐很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…总而言之…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天一整个晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都在我的房里…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有没有做出什么失礼的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-请问… -什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不记得吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,也并不是全都不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.21,0:22:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记的,因为我是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,请你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.76,0:22:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会逼你娶我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会追来这里找我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.75,0:23:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟他还是学生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也难怪他会累成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,想了的话我就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能想响子…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.70,0:23:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.84,0:23:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.21,0:23:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是他的马子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么下定决心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来可能撑不了几天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.42,0:23:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.75,0:23:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.35,0:23:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜…她怀孕了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.46,0:23:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,是三鹰教练的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是令人大吃一惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.86,0:23:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗,这是理所当然的结果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.13,0:24:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘明日菜怀孕? 三鹰惊人的结婚宣言!’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究…究竟是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.47,0:24:06.47,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.98,0:24:15.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}Begin the night Begin your love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.99,0:24:28.64,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}你该知道这不是擦身而过的恋情 亲吻也是…woo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.17,0:24:46.66,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}你比我想像中冷淡 喜欢一个人独处 沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.94,0:24:57.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}不要逞强 在这烛火依偎着的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.83,0:25:14.85,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}凝视着你的一切 试着将至今的谎言吹熄
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.55,0:25:22.11,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}Begin the night Begin your love
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.39,0:25:34.50,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}自我陶醉故弄玄虚 对我行不通…woo

